    /// ```yul
    /// group_by_exec_evaluate(plan_ptr, builder_ptr) -> plan_ptr_out, evaluations_ptr
    /// ```
    /// ##### Parameters
    /// * `plan_ptr` - calldata pointer to the group by execution plan
    /// * `builder_ptr` - memory pointer to the verification builder
